title: Onnanoko?
description:
1-4. A Girl? 
A strange disease is turning boys into big breasted nymphomaniacal girls.  The story is about a boy affected and the way he returns to normal.

5-9. Something Like That Too
High school life: friendship, romance, and gangbangs.

10. Pleasure Train
A girl riding a train sees another girl being raped nearby, but none of the other passengers seem to notice. What will happen to her?
